Behind the scenes

00:00:05.060 --> 00:00:06.800
of every movie you love

00:00:06.800 --> 00:00:09.080
years of planning have gone into making sure that

00:00:09.080 --> 00:00:13.300
every line, prop and camera angle are exactly what the film makers want.

00:00:13.780 --> 00:00:15.899
The crazy thing about movie making though,

00:00:15.899 --> 00:00:17.040
is that sometimes, even when with all the planning

00:00:17.080 --> 00:00:18.600
the film makers and actors decide to

00:00:18.600 --> 00:00:20.820
toss out the script and improvise instead.

00:00:20.920 --> 00:00:26.800
Sometimes this can be disastrous, but other times these unplanned moments turn out to be seriously awesome.

